kannada_original: ಎಲೆ ಕಾಂಡ ಹೂರೆಂಬೆ ಮಿಡಿಮೊಗ್ಗು ರಸದ ಫಲ
english_transliteration: Ele kāṇḍa hūrembe miḍimoggu rasada phala
english_translation: Leaf, stalk, flower-branch, half-bud, fruit of nectar
One is not like the other in structure or form.
How did this happen, whose skill/magic is this!

kannada_original: ಈ ನೆಲದ ಸೊಗಸು ಇದು – ಮುದ್ದು ರಾಮ.
english_transliteration: Ī nelada sogasu idu – Muddu Rāma.
english_translation: This is the charm of this earth – Muddu Rāma.
